  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#FAF8F5]">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-10 sm:px-16 lg:px-24">
      <p class="text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-6">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="font-playfair text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium text-[#2C2824] tracking-tight mb-12">Questions fréquentes</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <details class="group border-b border-black/10 pb-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[#2C2824] pr-8">Faut-il un niveau particulier en yoga, danse ou mouvement ?</h3>
            <span class="text-[#C4A855] group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-2xl">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base font-light text-[#2C2824]/70 leading-relaxed">
            Non. Les sessions du matin sont accessibles à tous, y compris si tu n'as jamais pratiqué. L'objectif n'est pas la performance mais d'arriver dans la journée détendu, ancré, disponible.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group border-b border-black/10 pb-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[#2C2824] pr-8">Le wifi est-il vraiment fiable ?</h3>
            <span class="text-[#C4A855] group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-2xl">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base font-light text-[#2C2824]/70 leading-relaxed">
            Oui. La fibre est installée et tient pour les visios et le travail à distance.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group border-b border-black/10 pb-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[#2C2824] pr-8">Combien de temps de travail effectif puis-je espérer ?</h3>
            <span class="text-[#C4A855] group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-2xl">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base font-light text-[#2C2824]/70 leading-relaxed">
            Deux plages de travail sont possibles chaque jour (matin et après-midi). Tu travailles autant que tu en as besoin — et si tu as besoin de temps off, tu prends du temps off. Le format reste flexible.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group border-b border-black/10 pb-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[#2C2824] pr-8">Comment se passent l'hébergement et les repas ?</h3>
            <span class="text-[#C4A855] group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-2xl">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base font-light text-[#2C2824]/70 leading-relaxed">
            Hébergement sur place inclus en tipi (2 lits simples par tipi, jusqu'à 2 personnes). Pension complète : trois repas par jour, faits maison, à partir des produits du jardin ou locaux (moins de 50 km). Préférences alimentaires et allergies prises en compte.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group border-b border-black/10 pb-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[#2C2824] pr-8">Puis-je venir en van ?</h3>
            <span class="text-[#C4A855] group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-2xl">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base font-light text-[#2C2824]/70 leading-relaxed">
            Oui, c'est possible. Tu peux te garer sur place et dormir dans ton van, avec accès aux espaces communs. Préviens-nous à la réservation pour qu'on s'organise.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group border-b border-black/10 pb-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[#2C2824] pr-8">Comment venir à LAOM ?</h3>
            <span class="text-[#C4A855] group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-2xl">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base font-light text-[#2C2824]/70 leading-relaxed">
            En train : gare de Montpaon, à 15 min en voiture (on peut venir te chercher).<br />
            En voiture : Montpellier 1h30, Toulouse 2h, Lyon 3h30. Du covoiturage est souvent organisé entre participants.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group border-b border-black/10 pb-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-[#2C2824] pr-8">Mon entreprise peut-elle financer le séjour ?</h3>
            <span class="text-[#C4A855] group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform text-2xl">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base font-light text-[#2C2824]/70 leading-relaxed">
            Oui. Beaucoup de participants font passer le séjour en frais professionnels (séminaire, retraite, formation). Une facture détaillée est fournie sur demande.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#2C2824] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-10 sm:px-16 lg:px-24 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#C4A855] mb-6">Places limitées</p>
      <h2 class="font-playfair text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-4 tracking-tight">Prêt·e à vivre l'expérience Chillworking à LAOM ?</h2>
      <p class="text-base font-light text-white/60 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Un séjour pour avancer sur ce qui compte vraiment, dans un cadre qui te ramène à toi.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <button
          type="button"
          data-open-reservation
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm bg-[#C4A855] text-white px-10 py-4 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase hover:bg-[#B09A4A] transition-colors cursor-pointer"
        >
          Je réserve ma place
        </button>
        <a
          href="https://cal.atomik.world/charly/30min"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-white/30 text-white px-10 py-4 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase hover:bg-white hover:text-[#2C2824] transition-colors"
        >
          Poser une question
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modal de réservation -->
  <dialog id="reservation-dialog" class="bg-transparent backdrop:bg-black/60 backdrop:backdrop-blur-sm p-0 max-w-2xl w-full mx-auto rounded-sm">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-sm shadow-2xl">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between p-6 md:p-8 border-b border-black/10">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-2">Réservation</p>
          <h2 class="font-playfair text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-[#2C2824]">Séjour Chillworking</h2>
        </div>
        <button type="button" id="close-reservation" aria-label="Fermer" class="text-[#2C2824]/40 hover:text-[#2C2824] transition-colors p-1 cursor-pointer">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <form id="reservation-form" class="p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6">
        <!-- Session -->
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-3">Session</label>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <label class="cursor-pointer">
              <input type="radio" name="session" value="juin" class="sr-only peer" checked />
              <div class="p-4 border-2 border-[#2C2824]/10 rounded-sm peer-checked:border-[#C4A855] peer-checked:bg-[#FAF8F5] transition-colors text-center">
                <p class="font-playfair text-base font-medium text-[#2C2824]">Juin 2026</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-light text-[#2C2824]/50 mt-1">15 — 28 juin</p>
              </div>
            </label>
            <label class="cursor-pointer">
              <input type="radio" name="session" value="aout" class="sr-only peer" />
              <div class="p-4 border-2 border-[#2C2824]/10 rounded-sm peer-checked:border-[#C4A855] peer-checked:bg-[#FAF8F5] transition-colors text-center">
                <p class="font-playfair text-base font-medium text-[#2C2824]">Août 2026</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-light text-[#2C2824]/50 mt-1">6 — 20 août</p>
              </div>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Date d'arrivée -->
        <div>
          <label for="arrivalDate" class="block text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-3">Date d'arrivée</label>
          <input
            type="date"
            id="arrivalDate"
            name="arrivalDate"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#2C2824]/15 rounded-sm focus:border-[#C4A855] focus:outline-none text-base text-[#2C2824]"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Nombre de nuits -->
        <div>
          <label for="nights" class="block text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-3">Nombre de nuits (5 min, 14 max)</label>
          <input
            type="number"
            id="nights"
            name="nights"
            min="5"
            max="14"
            value="7"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#2C2824]/15 rounded-sm focus:border-[#C4A855] focus:outline-none text-base text-[#2C2824]"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Coupon -->
        <div>
          <label for="coupon" class="block text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-3">Code promo (optionnel)</label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="coupon"
            name="coupon"
            placeholder=""
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#2C2824]/15 rounded-sm focus:border-[#C4A855] focus:outline-none text-base text-[#2C2824] uppercase"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Prénom + Nom -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <label for="firstName" class="block text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-3">Prénom</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="firstName"
              name="firstName"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#2C2824]/15 rounded-sm focus:border-[#C4A855] focus:outline-none text-base text-[#2C2824]"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="lastName" class="block text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-3">Nom</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="lastName"
              name="lastName"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#2C2824]/15 rounded-sm focus:border-[#C4A855] focus:outline-none text-base text-[#2C2824]"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Email -->
        <div>
          <label for="email" class="block text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-3">Email</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#2C2824]/15 rounded-sm focus:border-[#C4A855] focus:outline-none text-base text-[#2C2824]"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Téléphone -->
        <div>
          <label for="phone" class="block text-xs font-light tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-3">Téléphone</label>
          <input
            type="tel"
            id="phone"
            name="phone"
            required
            placeholder="+33 6 ..."
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#2C2824]/15 rounded-sm focus:border-[#C4A855] focus:outline-none text-base text-[#2C2824]"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Récap prix -->
        <div id="price-summary" class="p-5 bg-[#FAF8F5] rounded-sm space-y-2">
          <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-light text-[#2C2824]/70">
            <span id="price-base-label">Tarif de base</span>
            <span id="price-base">— €</span>
          </div>
          <div id="price-discount-row" class="flex justify-between text-sm font-light text-[#C4A855]" hidden>
            <span id="price-discount-label">Coupon</span>
            <span id="price-discount">— €</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-lg font-medium text-[#2C2824] pt-2 border-t border-black/10">
            <span>Total à régler</span>
            <span id="price-total">— €</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p id="form-error" class="text-sm text-red-600" hidden></p>

        <button
          type="submit"
          id="submit-btn"
          class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm bg-[#C4A855] text-white px-10 py-4 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase hover:bg-[#B09A4A] transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed cursor-pointer"
        >
          <span id="submit-label">Procéder au paiement sécurisé</span>
        </button>

        <p class="text-xs text-center font-light text-[#2C2824]/50">
          Paiement sécurisé via Mollie. Carte bancaire.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </dialog>

  <script>
    const dialog = document.getElementById('reservation-dialog') as HTMLDialogElement
    const closeBtn = document.getElementById('close-reservation')
    const form = document.getElementById('reservation-form') as HTMLFormElement
    const arrivalInput = document.getElementById('arrivalDate') as HTMLInputElement
    const nightsInput = document.getElementById('nights') as HTMLInputElement
    const couponInput = document.getElementById('coupon') as HTMLInputElement
    const sessionInputs = document.querySelectorAll('input[name="session"]') as NodeListOf<HTMLInputElement>
    const errorEl = document.getElementById('form-error') as HTMLParagraphElement
    const submitBtn = document.getElementById('submit-btn') as HTMLButtonElement
    const submitLabel = document.getElementById('submit-label') as HTMLSpanElement
    const priceBaseEl = document.getElementById('price-base') as HTMLSpanElement
    const priceBaseLabelEl = document.getElementById('price-base-label') as HTMLSpanElement
    const priceDiscountRow = document.getElementById('price-discount-row') as HTMLDivElement
    const priceDiscountEl = document.getElementById('price-discount') as HTMLSpanElement
    const priceTotalEl = document.getElementById('price-total') as HTMLSpanElement

    const SESSIONS = {
      juin: { start: '2026-06-15', end: '2026-06-28', label: 'Juin' },
      aout: { start: '2026-08-06', end: '2026-08-20', label: 'Août' },
    }

    function getSelectedSession(): 'juin' | 'aout' {
      const checked = Array.from(sessionInputs).find((i) => i.checked)
      return (checked?.value as 'juin' | 'aout') || 'juin'
    }

    function updateArrivalConstraints() {
      const sess = SESSIONS[getSelectedSession()]
      arrivalInput.min = sess.start
      // Max d'arrivée = end - nights jours (si départ < end)
      arrivalInput.max = sess.end
      if (!arrivalInput.value || arrivalInput.value < sess.start || arrivalInput.value > sess.end) {
        arrivalInput.value = sess.start
      }
    }

    function fmtEur(n: number) {
      return n.toLocaleString('fr-FR', { minimumFractionDigits: 0, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) + ' €'
    }

    function recalc() {
      const nights = parseInt(nightsInput.value || '0', 10)
      const couponRaw = (couponInput.value || '').trim().toUpperCase()
      if (!nights || nights < 5 || nights > 14) {
        priceBaseEl.textContent = '—'
        priceTotalEl.textContent = '—'
        priceDiscountRow.hidden = true
        return
      }
      const base = nights >= 12 ? 2000 : nights * 180
      priceBaseLabelEl.textContent = nights >= 12 ? `Forfait ${nights} nuits` : `${nights} nuits × 180 €`
      priceBaseEl.textContent = fmtEur(base)

      let discount = 0
      if (couponRaw === 'TRIBULAOM') {
        discount = Math.round(base * 0.2 * 100) / 100
        priceDiscountRow.hidden = false
        priceDiscountEl.textContent = '− ' + fmtEur(discount)
      } else {
        priceDiscountRow.hidden = true
      }
      const total = base - discount
      priceTotalEl.textContent = fmtEur(total)
    }

    document.querySelectorAll('[data-open-reservation]').forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        updateArrivalConstraints()
        recalc()
        errorEl.hidden = true
        dialog.showModal()
      })
    })

    closeBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => dialog.close())
    dialog?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      if (e.target === dialog) dialog.close()
    })

    sessionInputs.forEach((i) =>
      i.addEventListener('change', () => {
        updateArrivalConstraints()
        recalc()
      }),
    )
    nightsInput.addEventListener('input', recalc)
    couponInput.addEventListener('input', recalc)

    form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
      e.preventDefault()
      errorEl.hidden = true
      submitBtn.disabled = true
      submitLabel.textContent = 'Redirection vers le paiement…'

      const firstName = (document.getElementById('firstName') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim()
      const lastName = (document.getElementById('lastName') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim()
      const data = {
        product: 'chillworking',
        session: getSelectedSession(),
        nights: parseInt(nightsInput.value, 10),
        arrivalDate: arrivalInput.value,
        coupon: (couponInput.value || '').trim().toUpperCase() || undefined,
        firstName,
        lastName,
        name: `${firstName} ${lastName}`.trim(),
        email: (document.getElementById('email') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim(),
        phone: (document.getElementById('phone') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim(),
      }

      try {
        const res = await fetch('/api/mollie/create-payment/', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify(data),
        })
        const json = (await res.json()) as { checkoutUrl?: string; error?: string }
        if (!res.ok || !json.checkoutUrl) {
          throw new Error(json.error || 'Erreur inconnue')
        }
        window.location.href = json.checkoutUrl
      } catch (err: any) {
        errorEl.textContent = err?.message || 'Une erreur est survenue. Réessaie ou écris-nous.'
        errorEl.hidden = false
        submitBtn.disabled = false
        submitLabel.textContent = 'Procéder au paiement sécurisé'
      }
    })
  </script>

</Layout>
